JOB LIS.!ESPAPPL LINK PROCESS
  RUN DAILY
  DELAYSUB 8:00 AM
  RELEASE ADD(SWESPMBK)
ENDJOB

JOB SWESPMBK LINK PROCESS
  ESP OPER BKUPHIST HIST1
  ESP OPER BKUPEVS EVENT1
  ESP OPER BKUPINDX
  ESP OPER BKUPJNDX
  ESP OPER BKUPUDEF
  ESP OPER BKUPJSTS
  RUN DAILY
  RELEASE ADD(SWESPMSP)
ENDJOB

JOB SWESPMSP LINK PROCESS
  ESP OPER SPINLOG
  RUN DAILY
  RELEASE ADD(SWESP5SP)
ENDJOB

